<title type="html"><![CDATA[1/30(Sat.) Six leadership fundamentals from Michael Jordan &amp; Seven luck superstitions (Host: Larry)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=469&amp;p=487#p487"><![CDATA[
session 1<br />Six leadership fundamentals from Michael Jordan<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.inc.com/bernard-coleman/six-leadership-fundamentals-from-michael-jordan.html">https://www.inc.com/bernard-coleman/six ... ordan.html</a><!-- m --><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you think everyone can become a good leader as long as they meet the six requirements in the above article? <br />2.To be a good leader, in addition to the above conditions and characteristics, what other abilities do think are necessary?<br />3.Everyone know the importance of teamwork, if you are the boss or the person in charge, do you allowed to have different or opposed opinions, If so, how do you deal with it?<br />4.What do you think are the advantages or disadvantages of being a leader or a general worker?<br /><br />Session 2<br />Seven luck superstitions<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.thebalanceeveryday.com/lucky-superstitions-origin-895272">https://www.thebalanceeveryday.com/luck ... gin-895272</a><!-- m --><br />Questions:<br />1.In Taiwan, do you know any interesting and meaningful superstition? share them with us.<br />2.The lunar calendar plays an important role in Chinese culture, what do you do when you use it? If you don’t follow it, what will happen? For this, do you really believe it or not?<br />3.Taiwan has a ghost month in the lunar July, it is generally taboo to do any activities, would you follow it or not? Why?<br />4.There are wishing pools all over the world including Taiwan, if it can really fulfill your wish, what wish would you make?      <br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Sun Jan 24, 2021 4:39 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
